  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  TOKEN OVERRIDE SETTINGS REFERENCE
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  This file documents ALL available design token override
  settings that can be added to section/block schemas.

  NOTE: Shopify Liquid schemas are static JSON, so these
  settings must be manually added to each section's schema.
  Use this file as a copy-paste reference.

  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  USAGE:
    1. Add {% render 'section-tokens', settings: section.settings, section_id: section.id %}
       to the section's wrapper element or inside the section file.

    2. Copy the relevant settings group(s) below into the section's
       {% schema %} settings array.

  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  AVAILABLE SETTINGS GROUPS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

